				</div>
				<!-- /jumpto -->
								<!-- bodycontent -->
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p>The <b><a href="Historiography" title="Historiography">historiography</a> of early <a href="Islam" title="Islam">Islam</a></b> refers to the study of the early origins of Islam based on a critical analysis, evaluation, and examination of authentic <a href="Primary_source" title="Primary source">primary source</a> materials and the organization of these sources into a narative timeline.</p>
